        <prompt>What was the significance of the Comstock Lode discovery?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Sparked a major silver mining boom in Nevada</option>
            <option letter="b">Led to gold discoveries in California</option>
            <option letter="c">Created new farming territories</option>
            <option letter="d">Established oil drilling techniques</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Comstock Lode discovery in 1859 led to America's first major silver mining boom, dramatically affecting Nevada's development and national monetary policy.</explanation>
